text: Olkhovka () is a rural locality (a village) in Nikolayevsky Selsoviet, Tuymazinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 8 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 28 km from Tuymazy, 8 km from Nikolayevka. == References == Category:Rural localities in Tuymazinsky District
title: Olkhovka, Tuymazinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
